# Bug report

No matter how I "remove" the B008 warning in pyproject.toml (globally or on specific files), it is actually not ignored when running flakehell. Not sure if it's a bug on flakehell, WPS or flake8-bugbear side 😅 
I'm opening this here because flake8-bugbear is installed as a dependency of wemake-python-styleguide.

## What's wrong

**pyproject.toml:**
```toml
[tool.flakehell.plugins]
"*" = [
    "+*",
    "-B008",  # function calls in arguments defaults
]
```

```console
